list.name: Maurice
list.description: Maurice loves chocolate chip pancakes and eats them almost every Saturday. His dad makes a giant stack for Maurice and his sisters to share. One day, Maurice wants to be the host for a pancake show so he can try all kinds of pancakes.

list.name: Keely
list.description: Keely is a mommy blogger who wants to start her own painting business. She has painted murals for her friends and family, and dreams of one day painting a mural of her favorite place to visit - the Opera House! Want to see one of Keely's murals?

list.name: Skyler
list.description: Skyler is obsessed with gardening. He helps his grandmother and has developed quite the green thumb! He may give you a fright when you first meet him, but this skunk is a softie at heart.

list.name: Harrison
list.description: Harrison loves hockey, hiking, and horseback riding. He loves almost anything that involves being outdoors! Once a month Harrison is a counselor for Big/Little 'Mallows and brings the little 'Mallows on hikes.

list.name: Paco
list.description: Paco is quite the entertainer among his friends. You should see his dance moves! He's always up-to-date on current events and sports, especially soccer. Paco can't wait to be a sports broadcaster when he grows up!

list.name: Grant
list.description: This gutsy goat has one dream: to become a soccer player! Grant plays soccer at the park, at school, and at home with his friends. After winning a match, he always celebrates with a chocolate swirl cone!

list.name: Babs
list.description: Meet Babs. She loves superheroes, sci-fi, and created her own superhero, Captain Blueberry! Captain Blueberry is a regular bird by day and solves crime by night. Now Babs just needs to create a sidekick, what should she call them?

list.name: Tina
list.description: Tina's style is one for the books. Her patterned clothing isn't the only thing that stands out about this spunky 'Mallow. She is known for her unforgettable hairstyles that leaves everyone excited for their next hairdo!

list.name: Freddie
list.description: Games, guitars, and gumballs are some of Freddie's favorite things. When he isn't playing games with his friends you can find him practicing with his band - just don't step on his lucky guitar pic!

list.name: Cazlan
list.description: Did you see that flash of red soaring through the skies? It must be Cazlan! This speedy cardinal loves to zoom about but when she finally lands, it's time to get her nerd on with her best friend Babs. One day she wants to be her sidekick!

list.name: Todo
list.description: Have you ever wondered how to play the harmonica? Todd is a harmonica hero and can play almost any song he hears! Watch for him on the newest game show 'Play That Tune' to see if he's the next big harmonica sensation!

list.name: Chip
list.description: Chip is one smart 'Mallow! He's very kind and likes to help others. When Chip grows up, he wants to be an aircraft designer and fly the jets he creates!

list.name: Lockwood
list.description: Lockwood plays professional football! He's living his dream as a kicker playing for his favorite regional team. Lockwood thrives under pressure, and loves having a whole stadium watch him make a winning kick. Want tickets to this Sunday's game?

list.name: Celine
list.description: You might never meet a sweeter 'Mallow than Celine; she wants to help everyone she meets. Her aunt works for a nonprofit that helps 'Mallows in other parts of the world and when Celine grows up, she wants to work there too.

list.name: Rocky
list.description: Don't stop Rocky, he is on a roll! Rocky has been an adventure seeker since he was a little 'Mallow and plans on climbing his first summit this year. Grab a hiking stick and join in!

list.name: Trenton
list.description: Congratulations to Trenton! This amateur director Just took top honors at the local film festival. The critics loved his documentary about documentaries and can't wait to see what's next. According to Trenton, it's going to be a movie about movies!

list.name: Heather
list.description: True to her species' ability to transform, Heather is one of the mightiest 'Mallows around! No matter what obstacles come her way, she doesn't get discouraged. Heather can overcome any problems witha positive solution.

list.name: Priscilla
list.description: Have you met Priscilla? This perky peacock is always ready to lend a helping hand because she knows anything is possible! Priscilla loves to spend time with her friends and always finds new activities to try with them.

list.name: Terry
list.description: Gobble gobble, it's time for Terry's famous mashed garlic potatoes! Terry loves spending holidays with the foster family he grew up with and always makes sure to meet the current foster 'Mallows. They have a great time playing board games after dinner and always end the night knowing they're siblings for life!

list.name: Brenda
list.description: Brenda loves to be outside and enjoy the sun! She has a green thumb and sells flowers from her garden at the farmers market every week. Her favorite flowers are marigolds and phlox!

list.name: Teresa
list.description: Who loves the color purple, eating delicious food, and helping 'Mallows? Teresa! This busy unicorn is studying to be a doctor by day and is a foodie by night.

list.name: Kenny
list.description: Kenny is not your average dragon - he loves watching movies, going dancing, and learning about the world of finance! When he's not on the dance floor or catching the latest movie, he's studying for his Master's Degree.

list.name: Ukee
list.description: Ukee's booming voice can be heard from anywhere in the kitchen and beyond! This chef is serious about good food, so you better keep your wits about you if you're on the cooking line when Ukee's around. He can spot an overcooked egg from miles away!

list.name: Brindall
list.description: Meet Brindall. She doesn't just like hummus - she loves it! Brindall makes her own hummus from scratch with fresh herbs from her garden. This makes Brindall the perfect dinner party guest because she's guaranteed to bring a jar of her hmmus to share!

list.name: Eurydice
list.description: Eurydice is a high-school English teacher by day and a professional cosplayer by night. She loves combining her two worlds into one at the end of every class novel, when she'll come to school dressed as a character voted on by the students! This month, she has to construct a 'white whale' costume. Think she can do it?

list.name: Kya
list.description: Strawberry cupcakes and blueberry smoothies are two of Kya's favorite things! This koala has quite a sweet tooth and loves all desserts, especially ones with berries. Kya even adds frozen berries to her hot chocolate! She's an expert tree climber, and can pick mulberries from the treetops.

list.name: Brina
list.description: Say 'hi' to Brina the bigfoot! This confident little creature likes going on new adventures. Brina's favorite season is winter because her favorite sport is snowboarding! She waits all year to participate in the local snowboarding competition.

list.name: Benny
list.description: Benny is a bigfoot and one of the smartest creatures in the woods! He loves to run and play with his pals in the forest and beyond. When he is not running around, you can often find Benny taking photographs with woodland friends.

list.name: Lexis
list.description: Lexis loves attending hockey games with her sister, Erica. A certified history buff, Lexis enjoys knowing everything she can about the game. In fact, she knows so much that the local college asked her to teach a brand-new course - The Evolution of the Puck!

list.name: Dexter
list.description: Dexter is a unique individual who loves to fly around town with his friend, Brody. He dreams of being a pilot and traveling the world, but for now, Dexter sticks to soaring the skies around his neighborhood, and showing off some skills to his group of fun-loving fly friends!

list.name: Tatiana
list.description: Tatiana loves dancing, baking, and exploring with her friends. She wants to save the world one day at a time. Catch her with her friends out in the wild or in the library reading up on her next big adventure!

list.name: Sabrina
list.description: Sabrina is one of a kind! This caticorn travels the globe and has seen some amazing things. Sabrina wants to visit every single country, and will make sure to send you a postcard!

list.name: Ingred
list.description: Fifteen minutes to curtain! Ingred is an usher at the local theater. When she isn't showing 'Mallows to their seats, Ingred likes to stand at the back of the theater and memorize the routines of the dancers. One day, she hopes to make her way from the aisle to the stage!

list.name: Kayce
list.description: Have you ever seen a panda pegacorn do Muay Thai? Meet Kayce! She coaches soccer and trains in Muay Thai. On the weekends, Kayce loves to attend soccer tournaments and cheer on her favorite teams!

list.name: Ronalda
list.description: Don't let her horns fool you - Ronalda plays the strings! This musically-gifted 'Mallow is the principal violinist for the Yeti Philharmonic. Though some call her elusive, Ronalda is just busy. Between leading an orchestra and writing symphonies, who could blame her?

list.name: Magtus
list.description: Magtus collects lots of souvenirs from all over the world! But please ask him before taking one out of the cabinet. Magtus gets protective over these little treasures - even though some are as simple as coins or shells, it's still enough for Magtus to give you some side eye!

list.name: Noro
list.description: Do you like scary movies? Noro sure does! From ghosts in the closet to monsters on the roof, this boo-happy cthulhu has seen it all. He hopes to direct a frightening feature of his own one day and can't wait to hear the screams in the theater!

list.name: Nebula
list.description: Meet Nebula. She loves painting and learning about microorganisms. Nebula's parents are scientists and they gave her a microscope kit to learn more about the tiny organisms in her world. Sometimes she paints the cool things she sees and shares them with her friends. Can you name a microorganism she should paint?

list.name: Legacy
list.description: Meet Legacy. She has a beautiful butterfly garden which is pertect for frolicking amongst the flowers and keeping an eye out for new butterfiies. Legacy's favorite past time is laying in the grass and reading a book.

list.name: Davina
list.description: Though she's shy at first, Davina is a lot of fun. She does really great impressions and can almost always make you laugh. She wants to be a voiceover artist when she grows up. She has many voices and impressions that she just can't wait to try out.

list.name: Cam
list.description: Cam loves to jump in and out of boxes and build forts with his friends, Hoot and Wendy. He also enjoys going to the beach to take cat naps or hanging with his friends, but is always up for an adventure!

list.name: Wendy
list.description: You can either find Wendy in the science lab working on chemistry experiments, or on the basketball court-she won MVP last year! Wendy wants to be a famous scientist when she grows up. Want to see the drawing of her latest lab experiments?

list.name: Connor
list.description: Everyone mocooove out of the way, Connor is at the finish line waiting for you! This cow is quite the athlete, and you can usually catch him riding his bike all over town. Connor loves to travel, but do you know the coolest place he's ever been to? Cowlifornia!

list.name: Malcolm
list.description: Have you ever met a soccer-playing Mushroom? Malcolm is the one for you! He's the goalie on his team and they've won the championship three years in a row!

list.name: Mila
list.description: Mila is making moves! She has found her healthy fix through creative recipe tips, which she uses to treat her friends and family! Ready to get happy and healthy with Mila?

list.name: Sam
list.description: Sam is the friend for you, but only if you can keep up! He is a runner and can race circles around his friends at the park. He absolutely loves the outdoors and is always on the move.

list.name: Bernie
list.description: Bernie loves the mountains and helping other people more than anything else in the world. Bernie's dream is to become an EMT in order to assist in mountain rescues. When he's not saving lives, you will find Bernie enjoying the snowy weather. He keeps himself entertained by romping, rolling and pulling his friends on sleds!

list.name: Avery
list.description: Don't let his size fool you, Avery is a skilled left wingman for the 'Mallows rugby team and one day wants to be a coach! His whole family comes to watch and they bring popsicles to celebrate once the game is over.

list.name: Gregory
list.description: Meet Gregory, the go-to photographer for all things nature. Gregory takes amazing photos from all over the world, he just got back from a trip in the mountains! He loves sharing the amazing things he sees with other 'Mallows. Where should he go on his next photo-adventure?

list.name: Peter
list.description: Yes, you guessed it! Peter is quite the cuddly pig. He loves the wintertime and cuddling up with other pigs in a blanket. When he's not getting cozy, you can find him at a wrestling match or giving piggyback rides to his friends. Peter loves making new friends and is very good at keeping the old.

list.name: Stanley
list.description: Want a friend who will support and protect you? Well, you've got a friend in Stanley. He's been practicing karate since he was a little 'Mallow and even has his black belt test next month! When Stanley's not practicing his karate moves, you can find him writing new poems.

list.name: Hans
list.description: Hans is a movie buff - he's seen every movie ever! His favorite snack is popcorn with chocolate-covered raisins because when it comes to food, he's willing to try everything. Hans is very open to change and adventure.

list.name: Winston
list.description: Winston is an aspiring chef who takes his cooking creativity to the next level. His friends inspire his latest culinary delights and he is always ready to whip up his famous mac and cheese.

list.name: Lola
list.description: Lola loves the color pink, watching movies with her friends, and wants to be an actress when she grows up! She loves to visit new places and dreams of traveling the world making movies.

list.name: Fifi
list.description: Fifi is your 'Mallow if you like to go on adventures! Born October 6, she has a vibrant personality and is quite a little firecracker. Fifi channels her energy through yoga flows and is even working on getting her yoga teacher certificate!

list.name: Leonard
list.description: Have you ever met a lion who doesn't eat meat? Meet Leonard, he's a vegetarian! He loves lentils, eggplant lasagna, and learning how to code. Leonard is helping his older brother create his website. They make a great team!

list.name: Piper
list.description: Ready for hyper Piper? You will never see Piper without a paintbrush in her hand. She is quite artistic and is constantly creating new paintings in her art class. Piper loves to draw portraits and make friendship bracelets with her friends!

list.name: Simon
list.description: Want a buddy to just relax with? Simon is your perfect match. If you can't find him, he is probably at the store buying another video game! He is the greatest gamer on the block. Fun fact about Simon? He loves virtual reality. If it were up to him, he would teleport himself in a second!

list.name: Rosie
list.description: Meet Rosie, she's visiting her family from the other side of the pond! Rosie loves crunchy biscuits, going to concerts with her friends, and spending time with her nanna. Rosie's nanna makes the best tea and always has yummy treats ready when she comes over.

list.name: Puff
list.description: Puff loves melting cheese in his hot cocoa and sharing smiles with friends. He can also be a bit silly sometimes. But did you know, Puff is great at keeping secrets too! Wanna share some laughs

list.name: Perry
list.description: Hang 10 with Perry for the day and you're sure to become an avid surfer! When he's not surfing you can find him relaxing near the beach enjoying frozen yogurt and waxing his board for the next wave.

list.name: Samir
list.description: Who's that 'Mallow leading the pack? It's Samir! This wonderful whale never planned on being in charge but his kindness and consideration have helped him become an excellent leader. If you need some advice on making the best cholce, give Samir a call!

list.name: Archie
list.description: Have you met Archie? This shy 'Mallow has a special taient - he talks with his hands! Archie loves to play soccer and even started a club for 'Mallows to play and learn to Sign. Someday you might see him play in the 'Mallows Cup!

list.name: Stacy
list.description: Stacy is a shy squid and prefers to be home with her friends, or even by herself! Big groups of 'Mallows make her a little nervous, so she loves to learn and explore through books, Stacy might be quiet at first, but all her friends know she can be very silly.

list.name: Carlos
list.description: Have you met Carlos? This creative crustacean is a salsa instructor and world traveler. Carlos is a travel writer and writes about dance and food across the globe! His favorite travel food? Tapas!

list.name: Octavia
list.description: Meet Octavia, She has a helpful pep in her step just like ber sister, Jeanne! Octavia loves to paint nails and wants to open a nail salon for 'Mallows who cannot visit salons, but she doesn't know where to start. Will you help Octavia?

list.name: Violet
list.description: Violet is a bright and spirited queen of the sea with a passion for exploration. She loves to join Kai on his quests far sunken treasure, and uses her archaeology degree to identify where the treasure originated! Want to join Violet on one of her expeditions?

list.name: Matt
list.description: Did you see those crazy tee-shirt designs? Yes, Matt might have helped inspire the design! He loves graphic design + fashion and aspires to be a fashion designer one day.

list.name: Simone
list.description: Grab your spectacles and get ready for a musical journey, Simone is about to go on stage! Simone is an opera singer with a magical voice. You're always in for a treat if you can catch her while she's in town.
Living up to his species, Ricky knows how to make all the other 'Mallows laugh! Catch him at his next open mic night and see for yourself!

list.name: Bruce
list.description: Want to explore the beauty of the wilderness? Bruce is your 'Mallow! An active kayaker, Bruce leads travelers on amazing river tours and shows them all of his favorite hidden gems. Get ready for a photo op!

list.name: Lucille
list.description: Lucille loves living near the water! She always finds new creatures, hidden gems, and her favorite rocks whenever she goes on a dive. Ask to see her amazing rock collection!

list.name: Gordon
list.description: You don't have to fear, Gordon is one of the friendliest 'Mallows around! He loves helping others so much that one day he wants to start his own non-profit.

list.name: Henry
list.description: Known by all the 'Mallows for his fantastic voice, Henry is a famous sports announcer! While he regularly provides commentary on basketball, football, and baseball games, Henry's favorite sport is volleyball.

list.name: Maggie
list.description: Maggie is no ordinary stingray - she's a stingray with a degree! Maggie just received her degree in healthcare and can't wait to start helping others. This helpful stingray loves cooking, volleyball, and of course watching medical shows in her spare time.

list.name: Jayda
list.description: Jayda is a medical student who has a passion for helping others. She is also an expert at needlework. When she's not studying for exams, she's sketching designs and sewing costumes for her friends! What would you ask Jayda to sew for you?

list.name: Sheldon
list.description: Sheldon enjoys spending time by himself and learning more about the ocean he lives in! He loves learning about all the plants, other sea creatures, and making friends with the people he meets along the way. Fun fact about Sheldon: he wanted to be a jellyfish when he grew up!

list.name: Tank
list.description: Because of his size, Tank may look like a menacing 'Mallow, but he lives by the motto 'peace, love, and minding my business'. This hammerhead hippie wants to live in harmony and just enjoy life.

list.name: Shabnam
list.description: Shabnam is a civil engineer who loves to travel! She's always planning the next adventure for her family. For Shabnam, nothing is more important than her loved ones, so it's no wonder she's known for being one of the sea's sweetest 'Mallows.

list.name: Truman
list.description: Truman is a dentist who loves to travel. This turtle swims around the world offering dental care to all 'Mallows in need. Truman knows having teeth cleaned isn't easy for everyone, so he makes sure every cleaning is quick and even fun! Want to hear one of his classic knock-knock jokes?

list.name: Floyd
list.description: Have you ever met a french fry that loves adventure? Meet Floyd! This salty fry dreams of leaving the kitchen for adventures he's only heard about. Floyd wants to climb a mountain, sail the seas, or even visit his family out west!

list.name: Bernice
list.description: Blissful, bubbly, and bright are three words that describe the best boba you'll ever meet - Bernice! This 'Mailow is sweet, but not too sweet, and loves to help a friend in need. It's no wonder the word 'nice' is in her name!

list.name: Tex
list.description: Cheese, onions, and a little extra spice are some of Tex's favorite things. He's a chef who loves to use new ingredients to mix things up. Tex throws the best parties around, especially when his favorite toppings are in town! Will you join him at tonight's bash?

list.name: Maya
list.description: She's fresh, cool, with a hint of sweet - that's how all the 'Mallows describe Maya. This marvelous 'Mallow is the best ons to know if you need a helping hand. She'll give you a little tough love but always knows the right things to say to turn your frown upside down.

list.name: Maui
list.description: Skatebeards and scuba diving are two scary things Maui is determined to conquer her fear of. She already checked roller coastars and rollerblading off her list. Maui doesn't like to be scared so she tries to conquer her fears by trying new things. Can Maui help you overcome one of your fears?

list.name: Ausin
list.description: Austin loves drawing aliens and dreams of one day living in space! He loves pretending that he lives on the moon or Is climbing rock mountains on Mars. Austin became obsessed with outer space in school after reading a book about atiens. Will you help Austin plan his next space adventure?

list.name: Wanda
list.description: Wanda loves all things strategy - chess, dominoes, and making the perfect panini. When she visits her grandparents, they take her to play games in the park, and afterwards Wanda makes them her famous caprese panini.

list.name: Carl
list.description: Meet Carl. He loves practical jokes and hanging out with his burger bros. Ever since he was just a little patty, Carl has dreamed of being the funniest cheessburger in the pack! Wanna hear some of his new jokes?

list.name: Chanel
list.description: Meet Chanel. She's sweeter than your average pastry and she's a pastry chef who loves giving back! In her spare time, Chanel likes to volunteer at the local food pantry and teaches cake baking and decorating classes.

list.name: Sinclair
list.description: Sinclair and his cousin, Austin, love to talk about outer space. But they always disagree on whether aliens exist! Austin thinks they do, but Sinclair wants more proof. So, he agreed to join Austin on a space adventure to find out. Are you ready for liftoff

list.name: Carmelita
list.description: Do you like manga? You should check out some of Carmelita's work! She draws black and white manga about school, her life, and adventures with her best friend, Cinnamon. You won't have to worry about her spilling any secrets because Carmelita uses code names for any top secret friendship stuff!

list.name: Bernardo
list.description: Are you ready for a spicy surprise? Be sure to catch Bernardo on the baby grand piano every Friday night! He sings and plays the piano, but with a little twist - all his songs are in Spanish! And by the time you leave his show tonight, you might be singing in Spanish too!

list.name: Cinnamon
list.description: Cinnamon and her best friend Carmelita are like two peas in a pod, only sweeter! You can usually find them in the writing lab working on new stories, or at the mall window shopping. If you see Cinnamon out and about, she'll be sure to give you a big hug.

list.name: Mo
list.description: Hop in the car and buckle up! Mo is going to take you on an adventure. Mo is a tour guide and loves to drive around to show the hidden gems in the neighborhood.

list.name: Orin
list.description: Orin is a silly orange. He responds to questions with more questions and on Fridays he tries to do everything backwards! Thankfully, his friends like his silliness and play along with his jokes.

list.name: Ashley
list.description: Ashley loves table tennis - one day she wants to be part of the world's best table tennis team! For now, she practices with her friends and hosts backyard tournaments. You can help her keep score!

list.name: Phyllis
list.description: Have you met Phyllis? She is captain of the swimming team and can't wait to get back in the pool. If she could, she would turn into a mermaid!

list.name: Scarlet
list.description: Meet Scarlet. This sweet 'Mallow loves all things theater and dance, and wants to be both a performer and costume designer when she grows up. Scarlet's father taught her how to sew and every year she makes the costumes for her school's play! What's your favorite musical?

list.name: Leticia
list.description: Leticia is shyer than her brother, Leeland, but once she's got her racket, the game is on. Though they have very different personalities, they play tennis like one on the court. Watch out for her forehand!

list.name: Charles
list.description: You will usually find Charles working on a new drawing! He loves to doodle even if he doesn't have a specilic idea in mind. Sometimes, drawing reminds Charles of fun memories and his family who live in a faraway land. He can't wait to visit them this year!

list.name: Atwater
list.description: Atwater works at a boardwalk amusement park! She loves being seaside all day and helping little 'Mallows safely on and off the Ferris wheel, but her favorite perk is riding the wooden roller coaster as many times as she wants. Grab some cotton candy and hang around with Atwater!

list.name: Carizma
list.description: Meet Carizma, one of the coolest cats around! She loves to play the bass and practices almost every day. Carizma dreams of playing in a band with her friends and rocking a super trendy red and black mohawk! Want to watch her play?

list.name: Caedia
list.description: Grab your gloves and get ready for a workout! Caedia is a kickboxing instructor and has a stress-busting routine for everyone. Sometimes she even likes to write her students' problems on the punching bag for extra motivation. Would you take Caedia's kickboxing class?

list.name: Hadeon
list.description: Who has the prettiest kitchen in all the land? Hadeon does! He knows the heart of every home is the kitchen, so he spruced his up with decorative hanging pots, fruit plates, and a place setting just for you! Pull up a chair and let Hadeon whip you up a tasty meal!

Conradina is an amazing writer. She sees the world with vivid imagery and emotion. Now she's working up the courage to share her work. She wants to read in front of a crowd at open mic night, but public speaking makes her nervous. Can she practice reading a poem in front of you?

list.name: Dustin
list.description: Meet Dustin. This active little pup is always ready for adventure, He was once a rescue pup so he knows a thing or two about rescuing others. When he's not training for a flying disc contest, Dustin volunteers at the local fire station!

list.name: Mont
list.description: Mont isn't like most psychics - he's a dessert psychic! From brownies to baklava, this mystical 'Mallow can see into the future of any sweet treat. Though that future usually involves his stomach, he has yet to be wrong!

list.name: Francine
list.description: Francine has never missed a corn maze tour! Every year she hops through the huge corn maze outside town with her trusty map. It's such a fun tradition! Francine hopes to be a tour guide when she gets older, and share the joy with younger 'Mallows experiencing their first corn maze.

list.name: Mully
list.description: Say hi to Mully! Mully is a folk-music-loving mushroom. If you're ever feeling low, Mully will make you smile by strumming you a song on his banjo. If you're lucky, he might even play you a tune on his harmonica, too!

list.name: Shelly
list.description: Shelly runs a frightfully fabulous jewelry store! From spiderweb wedding rings to skeleton-bone broaches. her drop-dead gorgeous designs are the talk of the graveyard. Check out Shelly's earthworm earrings- they're a real scream!

list.name: Sydnee
list.description: Meet Sydnee! This super squirrel dreams of becoming a super spy. She loves watching mystery movies with her family and even assigned them all code names. Make sure to check out Sydnee's secret headquarters - the treehouse in her backyard!

list.name: Delzi
list.description: Delzi just started taking pottery classes and now she can't stop making mugs! Delzi finds pottery throwing so relaxing and fun. She even loves how messy it gets! She's decided to save up to buy a pottery wheel of her own. Would you like Delzi to make you a personalized mug?

list.name: Eileen
list.description: Eileen started a community event called Spring Seeds. On the first day of spring, town residents are encouraged to plant a seed of anything they like and share the growth progress throughout the year. Eileen even sends pictures of her sprouting plant to the weekly paper. Imagine all the gorgeous gardens this will create!

list.name: Goldine
list.description: Goldine works at the local news station, hooking up mics and mixing sound. She records sound for the morning news and a live talk show that follows it. Goldine has very early mornings, but when she clocks out, there is so much left of the day! Would you like to spend the afternoon with Goldine?

list.name: Griella
list.description: Meet Griella. They love lazy Sundays and breakfast in bed. In the afternoon, they hit up their favorite sandwich shop and order the #7 with extra pastrami. At night, Griella loves concerts, karaoke, or a long car ride with loud music. They know all the words so come sing along!

list.name: Ileana
list.description: Ileana visits her local botanical garden every spring! She loves to see all the beautiful flowers in bloom. Ileana brought her bestie, Sherry, to the botanical garden today, and they're wearing bunny ears to make the trip extra festive.

list.name: Iver
list.description: Iver has dozens of different herbal teas in his kitchen- it's his favorite drink in the world! Iver likes blending different teas together to create new concoctions, like blueberry mint chamomile and red apple rooibos. But he thinks his best creation so far is ginger lemon ginseng! Come share a pot of tea with Iver.

list.name: Reina
list.description: Meet Reina. This fabulaus butterfly loves fashion, fun, and drawing. Her love for fashion inspires many of her heautiful creations, and you might even see her artwork on the cover of a magazine some day!

list.name: Satine
list.description: Satine is a total brunch bunny! She orders way too much food and packs whatevar is left over to save for later. Satine hangs out all morning with orange juice and coffee, either reading the morning paper or chatting with a buddy. Join Satine and don't forget to bring your appetite!

list.name: Rorty
list.description: Meet Rorty. This cuddly monster is always up for a movie night with his friends. His favorite movies are rom-coms, and he even dreams of starring in his own movie when he grows up! So grab a bowl of popcorn, some fuzzy slippers, and join Rorty on the couch for a movie night!

list.name: Johanna
list.description: Johanna loves when the air turns crisp and the leaves on the trees begin to change. It means all her favorite fall vegetables are in season! Johanna loves to cook hearty soups that keep her and her friends warm during the cool fall nights. So grab a bowl, she'd love to share!

list.name: Holly
list.description: Every year Holly has a Halloween party-there's a costume contest, an apple cider tasting, and even pumpkin carving! Holly just needs help deciding what costume to wear. Can you help her decide?

list.name: Wade
list.description: Wade is a werewolf! While he understands that can be frightening for some, Wade hopes to show the world he's just like everyone else. This gentle giant loves helping his friends, participating in beach clean-ups, and playing the violin! Want to come to his next recital?

list.name: Stump
list.description: Stump works security for his favorite band, Skeleton Squad. This 'Mallow knows a thing or two about keeping the Squad safe! When the band isn't touring, Stump teaches a spooky self-defense class. Don't forget, costumes are encouraged

list.name: Alva
list.description: Alva stumbles into wacky situations everywhere she goes. Some memorable experiences include the time she found the end of a rainbow, the summer she discovered a secret treasure map, and when she saw a ghost in her bathtub on Halloween! Alva can't explain these moments-she's just a 'Mallow with good timing.

list.name: Cam
list.description: Cam loves to jump in and out of boxes and build forts with his friends, Hoot and Wendy. He also enjoys going to the beach to take cat naps or hanging with his friends, but is always up for an adventure!

list.name: Blas
list.description: Blas rakes the fallen autumn leaves in front of his home every day. When he's done, it's time to jump in! Blas loves the crunchy sound of leaves as he flies into a great big pile. Come join Blas and his 'Mallow pals for some fall fun!

list.name: Carina
list.description: Maybe Carina watched too many TV shows about UFOs, because now she's on a mission to find one! Carina loves space and astronomy more than any other subject, and dreams of one day seeing a UFO with her own eyes. Wanna go UFO hunting tonight with Carina?

list.name: Lucasta
list.description: Lucasta freaked out last year at the Halloween fair and went home early-but not this year! Lucasta promised herself she would be a brave bat all night, even on the super scary haunted house ride. She brought her pal, Ramably, so they can laugh out loud during all the creepy sound effects!

list.name: Ernesto
list.description: Watch out for Ernesto! This 'Mallow moves fast on the soccer field, and before you know it, he's scored! Ernesto plays the midfield position, and will use his signature header to knock in goals. Ernesto loves the game, but loves supporting his teammates most of all.

list.name: Evita
list.description: Want to join Evita on her next wilderness adventure? This 'Mallow never gets cold, and has been known to hike through snowstorms! Grab your snowshoes and start catching snowflakes with Evita.

list.name: Farryn
list.description: Meet Farryn. She loves to jump in puddles and listen to the rain while she falls asleep. Farryn loves storms and wants to learn more about all the things weather can do. You can always find her watching storm chaser shows, and Farryn even thinks she would make a great storm chaser when she grows up!

list.name: Johanna
list.description: Do you like to celebrate the season? So does Johann. This super creative pine tree loves dressing up for different holidays. Though most 'Mallows associate him with Christmas, Johann has an outfil for every occasion. His favorite is Halloween!

list.name: Jones
list.description: Have you been wronged by cracked gingerbread? Wrinkly wrapping paper? Wilted mistletoe? Call Jones, Attorney at Paw. An expert on hotiday law, this persuasive feline doesn't just fight the naughty-he defends the nice!

list.name: Lowell
list.description: Lowell goes out caroling every winter. At first they got nervous singing in public, but now Lowell is as confident as ever! Caroling with friends around town or under the gazebo at the park has become one of Lowell's favorite traditions. Will you join Lowell's caroling group this year?

list.name: Manny
list.description: Manny is a budding engineer. This crafty 'Mallow dreams of using science and creativily to make the world a better piace! Though he has a lot left to learn, Manny is already putting his talents to work. Last winter, he built a gingerbread house with flickering holiday lights!

list.name: Peterson
list.description: Peterson drives a big pickup truck-the same one he's been driving for years. Sometimes it goes on the fritz and Peterson has to make repairs, but this cookie doesn't mind one bit. His truck helps everyone around town with moves of all sizes, making Peterson's pickup truck as beloved as he is.

list.name: Joyce
list.description: The only thing Joyce loves more than shopping for herself is shopping for others. A personal stylist at her favorite boutique, Joyce takes joy in heiping other 'Mallows decide what to wear and how to wear it!

list.name: Cam
list.description: Cam loves to jump in and out of boxes and build forts with his friends, Hoot and Wendy. He also enjoys going to the beach to take cat naps or hanging with his friends, but is always up for an adventure!

list.name: Hans
list.description: Hans is a movie buff - he's seen every movie ever! His favorite snack is popcorn with chocolate-covered raisins because when it comes to food, he's willing to try everything. Hans is very open to change and adventure.

list.name: Gordon
list.description: You don't have to fear, Gordon is one of the friendliest 'Mallows around! He loves helping others so much that one day he wants to start his own non-profit.

list.name: Archie
list.description: Have you met Archie? This shy 'Mallow has a special talent-he talks with his hands! Archie loves to play soccer and even started a club for 'Mallows to play and learn to Sign. Someday you might see him play in the 'Mallows Cup!

list.name: Winston
list.description: Winston is an aspiring chef who takes his cooking creativity to the next level. His friends inspire his latest culinary delights and he is always ready to whip up his famous mac and cheese.

list.name: Lola

list.name: Fifi
list.description: Fifi is your 'Mallow if you like to go on adventures! Born October 6, she has a vibrant personality and is quite a little firecracker. Fifi channels her energy through yoga flows and is even working on getting her yoga teacher certificate!

list.name: Avery
list.description: Don't let his size fool you, Avery is a skilled left wingman for the 'Mallows rugby team and one day wants to be a coach! His whole family comes to watch and they bring popsicles to celebrate once the game is over.

list.name: Malcom
list.description: Have you ever met a soccer-playing Mushroom? Malcolm is the one for you! He's the goalie on his team and they'vewon the championship three years in a row!

list.name: Maui
list.description: Skateboards and scuba diving are two scary things Maui is determined to conquer her fear of. She already checked roller coasters and rollerblading off her fist. Maui doesn't like to be scared so she tries to conquer her fears by trying new things. Can Maui help you overcome one of your fears?

list.description: Lola loves the color pink, watching movies with her friends, and wants to be an actress when she grows up! She loves to visit new places and dreams of traveling the world making movies.
